dismissalText.commentary: Umar Bhatti run out (Mishra/Ouma) 1 (2b 0x4 0x6 4m) SR: 50

dismissalComment.html: horrible flash - stepping back to that one for a waft. But, hello, some even more horrible cricket... The keeper lobbed it back to the bowler, but it went over his head, and the covering fielder returned to the keeper. Meanwhile, Bhatti had decided the run was on, but was left stranded when Dhaniram refused to set off. Oh dear
